name: DefaultedMap_getTest
description: Unit tests for the get method of the DefaultedMap class, which tests various scenarios including existing keys, non-existing keys, null keys, and changes in default transformers.

test_cases.name: testGetExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for an existing key.

test_cases.name: testGetNonExistingKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for a non-existing key, expecting the default value.

test_cases.name: testGetNonExistingKeyWithDefault
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for a non-existing key, expecting the default value.

test_cases.name: testGetWithNullKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for a null key, expecting the default value.

test_cases.name: testGetWithNullKeyAndDefault
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for a null key after putting a value for null, expecting the put value.

test_cases.name: testGetWithDefaultTransformer
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap with a new default transformer for a non-existing key.

test_cases.name: testGetWithExistingKeyAfterDefaultTransformerChange
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for an existing key after changing the default transformer.

test_cases.name: testGetWithNonExistingKeyAfterDefaultTransformerChange
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for a non-existing key after changing the default transformer.

test_cases.name: testGetWithDefaultTransformerAndNullKey
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for a null key with a new default transformer.

test_cases.name: testGetWithDefaultTransformerAndNullKeyAfterPut
test_cases.description: Tests the get method of DefaultedMap for a null key after putting a value for null with a new default transformer.
